{"tid":630954,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]TPE48 冼迪琦男朋友現身 各位港台毒撚死心啦","createTime":"2018-04-16T05:06:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T16:05:33.000Z","uid":136729,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"1746654840b9276c45ae1bb3b9615f49c1a6d516","tid":630954,"uid":136729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:06:41.000Z","msg":"冼迪琦（Kitty Sin，1999年2月13號&mdash;），係童星出身嘅香港女演員，2005年因參加《殘酷一叮》而成為香港無綫電視童星，出演過唔少劇集，例如《巨輪》、《蘭花劫》、《烈火雄心3》飾雯雯、《仁心解碼》飾陳美娟（童年）、《學警狙擊》飾江悠悠（童年）。2018年，佢獲選做日本偶像團體AKB48喺臺灣嘅姊妹團TPE48頭一批香港成員<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/16/130613_cdc085b07a28aa3e15942aa10017baba.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F16%2F130613_cdc085b07a28aa3e15942aa10017baba.png&h=46f62aa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbb14b7e131f00dc3d7c8615ab69e9beeda252ae","tid":630954,"uid":136729,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5801b6ae6d3326c3787908378ec9c32c3d4f2430","tid":630954,"uid":116530,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:09:09.000Z","msg":"TPE48 狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"050aeb818825eaf06f4c6346bc4eff5f35feadf1","tid":630954,"uid":136729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5801b6ae6d3326c3787908378ec9c32c3d4f2430","tid":630954,"uid":116530,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:09:09.000Z","msg":"TPE48 狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:12:19.000Z","msg":"Tbb童星<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b87e7382fa51e67fc64ddffd78c058c5e407f16","tid":630954,"uid":136729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:18:59.000Z","msg":"東網約了其中5名入圍的香港參加者，分別是陳盈臻、林裕君、陳嘉希、劉曉晴及冼迪琦。她們年紀輕輕，分別只有17至22歲。由香港走到台灣參加徵選活動，只因為兩個字　－　追夢。於香港這個相對現實的社會，大家可能覺得她們不切實際，「讀好啲書先啦」。不過，青春就是本錢。她們由細到大都鍾情AKB48，難得機會近在眼前。5位小妮子一於少理，希望珍惜眼前的機會，成為TPE48的一員，於舞台上發熱發亮。 <br />\n<br />\n「每個人都有自己叻嘅嘢，有自己嘅天地，你唔試，就唔知自己係咪可以。如果當初冇報名，都唔知自己可以入到第3輪。」陳嘉希雖然年紀小，但說這番話時，大大的眼睛令她堅定的眼神更加突出。陳的家人一開始反對她報名，「話我發夢」，不過她的堅持最後亦令家人妥協。至於陳盈臻參加徵選活動，不單止因為鍾情日本文化，更因為受媽媽的影響。「我媽後生時喺日本讀過書，令我好有憧憬。」 <br />\n<br />\n5位入圍的香港參加者，殺入TPE48徵選活動的第三階段審查，不少港人亦有留意，頓時成為網民的討論對象。不過，她們都冇有怕，特別是曾做童星的冼迪琦。「細個拍過劇集同廣告，有好多『黑材料』，細個好肥、帶眼鏡，預咗會畀人拎出嚟，有晒心理準備。」"},{"pid":"4cf97f5e6aeeb49c7fc203fa1a0de0a03a6da39a","tid":630954,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:21:46.000Z","msg":"我女神呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a2a70c9a1b54da05fda75e95194e448fc71b31","tid":630954,"uid":136729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4cf97f5e6aeeb49c7fc203fa1a0de0a03a6da39a","tid":630954,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:21:46.000Z","msg":"我女神呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:34:22.000Z","msg":"你女神無了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90217d662790ca02c8bc1ff933bcc57356a98ed6","tid":630954,"uid":96704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T06:15:59.000Z","msg":"咁靚女冇男朋友先奇啦"},{"pid":"413ed0edbf4a652ec86f5fd80cf3740ad03da883","tid":630954,"uid":41508,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T06:26:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f04ff4905eedbb32e992bfdf742cd67bc39c2c8","tid":630954,"uid":152589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T06:29:25.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"712ef5c3e